title: Nipples Ruled This Season’s Runways (NSFW)
text:
View Slideshow
If there's one runway trend you can rely on blossoming season after season , it's nipples. They showed up more than 200 times this past fashion month, and while some designers were repeat offenders, boobs were out pretty much across the board. For small-chested models and #freethenipple supporters, this is great news; for the rest of us, well, at least it's amusing?
Designers may not have you covered, but the Cut does: Click through the slideshow to see our picks for the 75 best instances of this season's least expensive accessory, featuring Alexander McQueen , Céline , Saint Laurent , and Valentino .
